Exclusion criteria:

1. Mini Mental State Test score ≤ 24;
2. Mental illness;
3. Contra-indications to rTMS according to guidelines formulated by Wassermann (e.g., intracranial implants, epilepsy, cardiac pacemaker, implanted medication pumps); 4 Unstable cardio-pulmonary condition.
